    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "[Yarn](https://classic.yarnpkg.com/lang/en/docs/install) (`npm i -g yarn`)은 프로젝트를 빌드하거나 개발 서버를 직접 실행하려면 필요합니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "P37kvIEtIXMGJStnkUnXqtN7DEZo6cK21NbrQACctzA=",
    "originContent": "[Yarn](https://classic.yarnpkg.com/lang/en/docs/install) (`npm i -g yarn`) is required if you wish to build the project or run the development server yourself.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
